cross: Sarcochilus hartmannii x Sarcochilus Kulnura Sanctuary

measurements.description: Three hundred eight flowers and 85 buds on 26 20-cm inflorescences; plant 40cm wide by 25cm tall, grown in 18-cm pot, bark media; sepals and petal white, pink markings distally, concentrated dark pink markings proximally; lip yellow, pink spots; substance firm; texture matte.
